    "bank": "clinicalTherapeutics",
    "title": "**Theme: Drugs used in musculoskeletal and joint diseases**\u2028\r\n\r\n**Instruction: For each of the scenarios below, select the single most appropriate drug from the list of options. Each option may be used once, more than once, or not at all.**",
